Once upon a time in a forest there live a Monkey who recided on a Berry Tree, which was on a bank of a river.In the same forest there lived a Crocodile 
and his Wife. One day,The crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree.The kind hearted Monkey offered him some food. The crocodile came back the next day for more fruits ,
as he loved them.As days passed by,the crocodile and the Monkeybecame good friends.
